Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育园今天有义卖会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是...五百祗...先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副模样除了我还能是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是本大爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一直用手按着不放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土...鸠...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在大街上睡午觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果困了 还是回家进被窝好好睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才 才 才不是在睡午觉!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:14.17,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組

Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}该怎么办才好来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:14.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:14.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所当然的事情总是这么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纷繁复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想开心的时候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:25.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:25.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的时候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:28.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:34.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:34.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常说愿望总会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:41.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:41.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是总会到底要多久　已经等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:52.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:52.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告诉我在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}伤得满目疮痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:08.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}几十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是这样还
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:15.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:15.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}难以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:19.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:19.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信着明天

