Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...谜之生命体.2号.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生 这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见我这个样子还不明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生不知怎么满身是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都看不出来吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 听我说!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天阴沉沉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿肯定能卖出去的东西过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有肯定能卖出去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在保育园装布偶也差不多腻味了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去熊那里大吃一顿年轮蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是开在这种奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(熊记年轮蛋糕店)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(正在营业中)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个长蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我4个热香饼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个香草的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了 热香饼三人份 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候 正在烤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热香饼六个装做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长蛋糕怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 还要2分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是生意兴隆啊 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是瑞祥的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了功夫就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再增加些品种吧 巧克力什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坏嘛 就那么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真成蛋糕师了啊 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初还以为会变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的就顺其自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连挖苦都不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 对了 宅配服务也开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是熊记年轮蛋糕店吗 等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?不是平时一直来的那位鸟先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...这样啊 是兼职的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经也有过拼命兼职的时期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恣意妄为的雇主使唤来使唤去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话就这么多吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去过像迷宫之馆一样的那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个不可思议的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间多得让人迷路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(休息中)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你们现在这副悠然自得的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快把你们以前是什么样的都忘了啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体也不坏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛太厚是有点不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过注意点的话也没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得我从出生起一直是这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然发生过那种事 简直就像梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经过去很久了呢 从那以来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静地想一想 我们根本没有胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手太厉害了 根本是在被动挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溃败得也真是快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候好像踩到谁了 是谁来的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?!是玄琥大人吗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且当时也没空为了那些小事发火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的我们啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什么也别说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不认同 规矩就是规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能一边烤年轮蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边等时间来解决问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是反省的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了这种可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不能想也不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再跟天界开打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可就不是熊啊小鸟的就算完得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让我变成泰迪熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他就不用变鸟了 变成鸟食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那可不要的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己变成可爱的角色太狡猾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 总之 麻烦是无论如何绝对不要惹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 别吃啊 那是我重要的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果手信也只肯给一盒 小气鬼熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 吃了甜的再来点咸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 吃了咸的再吃这个年轮蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有咸的东西呢?没有呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过酱油味也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在这心情还是盐味合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 就是能有种冲击感的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我解围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 球又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它那么多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要命 臭小鬼都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就踢个球有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是你们的食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 这是本大爷的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还配不上吃年轮蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就此收手的话就把你们变成烤全...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~咧~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可太吃力了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快把火以外的东西吐出来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子好重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪上加霜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那东西的话就可以一口气弄干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干燥机里比想象中要艰苦得多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...什么地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那里的蔬菜店...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 肚子饿了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要留到回去之后慢慢享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是忍不住要先吃的小鬼..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这闻上去很香的气味是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那迷之生命体是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到mocono land
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宵的ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要高兴地忘乎所以然后迷路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就请尽情玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来闯进了奇怪的地方了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那香味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!哪个看起来都很好吃的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说了我是布偶又不是布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点逃出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被别人把年轮蛋糕的盒子拿走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要哪个都没问题的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打靶啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要那个蓝色的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?我看看...我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 没打中 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了 这回...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线冲我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又没中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这回一定能中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?感觉它是不是动了下?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会动嘛 是爸爸不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是打不中 爸爸越是燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一定会弄到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下一发会怎么样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 身为一个成年人不要那么认真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给老朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看老朽这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是被称为靶神加奈的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪冒出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦 不倒下的话是不算的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么大家齐心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只蓝色的还没倒下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要变成小孩子的玩具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了啊 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 刚刚是掉下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 大家也都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 倒霉透顶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里的话就稍微能放心...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是发生了这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为海报被人撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直跑到这个时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有人来义卖会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那个规模也太小了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算海报不被人撕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个保育园的拍卖会也不该抱太大期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道会变成这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是当时不说要办义卖会才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是决定了要做就要好好做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇到困难也不可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是被水弄湿 被狙击手狙击也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 最重要的就是要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为没有客人就那么失望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 卖掉了这么多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃也卖出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小鸠 我也淘到了好东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在那发呆发到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么多的客人 人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小鸠的努力 才有这么多客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没那种事..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了小鸠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你特意过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也买了不少有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实很希望从小鸠手里买到东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有卖自己的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖的怎么样了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也没卖出去...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不知是鸡是企鹅还是羊的谜之生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我买一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是很有个性的设计呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂 堂元先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是美好的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是过的很悲惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你有没有听本大爷说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是这样吗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 嘛 保住了那件重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果来说还是好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以后马上开吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要好好品尝那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是哪个呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了 本大爷的年轮蛋糕没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 回去保育园拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 年轮蛋糕的话早卖掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生说了要拿能卖的东西回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个能卖的东西就是指年轮蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的分数...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对义卖会的热情八十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上让我失望的扣分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合计分数是负三百分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失望是我的错吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是道歉就能解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把我做的可爱小兔子送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 作为赠品多送给你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加上这边可爱的小熊和小羊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来这个哪个是哪个根本就分不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一堆都是迷之生命体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?太过分了五百祗先生

Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...寒风的温暖.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
